Tiny tanks! The perfect thing to give a sense of scale to your tiny titans, tiny aircraft, or tiny anything! Add them as base decoration, add them as terrain decoration, create tiny war dioramas, do whatever you want with them! Anything is made better with the addition of tiny tanks.

Here comes the tiny portable poppity ping! Looks like your tiny enemies made a glaive mistake! Just put them in for four minutes at 100% power (pause to stir midway through!) and any tiny foe will be thoroughly cooked! Convenience in the palm of your hand. No need to mess about with preheating the oven, just point the tiny microwave in the right direction and watch it go.

Tiny tanks are intended for resin printers.
